Blue Stinger takes off flying after Unitron and shoots missiles at him. She 
sweeps under Anubis's missile and keeps firing.

Key jumps out of the way of the rocket, firing another shot at Koga Shuko.

Antagony flies back as several shots hit her torso. She stands up, firing a 
shot at Anubis. She fires another shot when she sees Sona fly up behind 
Anubis and shooting her sonar gun at him.
